Package: sqlConnect
Type: Package
Title: Convenient Table Accessors for DBI Connections
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Jiefei", "Wang", , "szwjf08@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides an S4 wrapper around DBI connections to discover schemas,
    list tables, and access database tables with `$` and `[[` operators. The
    package includes backend-aware metadata queries for Oracle, PostgreSQL, SQL
    Server, MySQL, SQLite, and Snowflake, with optional table-name caching for
    interactive workflows.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    DBI,
    dplyr,
    glue,
    methods
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
